<bibRefCitation id="658E73C6FC957FB111B801B8D5F9A70A" DOI="https://doi.org/10.11609/JoTT.o2783.2499-509" author="Sreeraj, CR" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Threatened Taxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" pagination="2499 - 2509" refId="B56" refString="Sreeraj, CR, Chandrakasan, S, Raghunathan, C, 2012. An annotated checklist of opisthobranch fauna (Gastropoda: Opisthobranchia) of the Nicobar Islands, India. Journal of Threatened Taxa 4: 2499 - 2509, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11609/JoTT.o2783.2499-509" title="An annotated checklist of opisthobranch fauna (Gastropoda: Opisthobranchia) of the Nicobar Islands, India." url="https://doi.org/10.11609/JoTT.o2783.2499-509" volume="4" year="2012">Sreeraj et al. 2012</bibRefCitation>
), Maldives (
<bibRefCitation id="90E85828946B870AF36B1D7AA6D8EBEE" author="Yonow, N" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Conchology" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" refId="B67" refString="Yonow, N, 1994b. Opisthobranchs from the Maldive Islands, including descriptions of seven new species (Mollusca: Gastropoda). Revue francaise d'aquariologie (1993) 20: 97-129." title="Opisthobranchs from the Maldive Islands, including descriptions of seven new species (Mollusca: Gastropoda). Revue francaise d'aquariologie (1993) 20: 97 - 129." year="1994 b">Yonow 1994b</bibRefCitation>
