<bibRefCitation id="C18005F6D11DF0F589050386B91907E8" DOI="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1042.64474" author="Mehrotra, R" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" pagination="73 - 188" refId="B42" refString="Mehrotra, R, Caballer Gutierrez, MA, Scott, CM, Arnold, S, Monchanin, C, Viyakarn, V, Chavanich, C, 2021. An updated inventory of sea slugs from Koh Tao, Thailand, with notes on their ecology and a dramatic biodiversity increase for Thai waters. ZooKeys 1042: 73 - 188, DOI: https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1042.64474" title="An updated inventory of sea slugs from Koh Tao, Thailand, with notes on their ecology and a dramatic biodiversity increase for Thai waters." url="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1042.64474" volume="1042" year="2021">Mehrotra et al. 2021</bibRefCitation>
