<bibRefCitation id="742208D190CBFD164274F8CBB8805CF2" author="Sanpanich, K" journalOrPublisher="Phuket Marine Biological Center Research Bulletin" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" pagination="45 - 60" refId="B53" refString="Sanpanich, K, Duangdee, T, 2019. A survey of marine mollusc diversity in the Southern Mergui archipelago, Myanmar. Phuket Marine Biological Center Research Bulletin 75: 45 - 60" title="A survey of marine mollusc diversity in the Southern Mergui archipelago, Myanmar." volume="75" year="2019">Sanpanich and Duangdee 2019</bibRefCitation>
